# Apex CRM Core Rules

## Backend Tier

Express server (`server.js`) serves the static HTML frontend and JSON API from the project root.

- **CRITICAL PRESERVATION:** Never remove, overwrite, or simplify the global dynamic HTML file serving fallback route or static asset middleware in `server.js`. All routing modifications must append new API endpoints strictly without cleaning or touching static file delivery loops.
